","$L47",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"Uy-joy sotib olganda mulkiy chegirma qancha?"}],["$","$L48",null,{"children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"Chegirma 500 BHK gacha (2025-yil avgustidan 206 000 000 so'm). Umr davomida bir marta beriladi."}]}]]}],["$","$L46","5",{"value":"faq-5","children":[["$","$L47",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"IT Park xodimlari uchun JShShS qanday farq qiladi?"}],["$","$L48",null,{"children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"IT Park rezidentlari 12% o'rniga 7,5% stavkada JShShS to'laydilar. 10 mln so'm ish haqida oylik tejamkorlik 450 000 so'm."}]}]]}],["$","$L46","6",{"value":"faq-6","children":[["$","$L47",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"JShShSni to'lamaganlik uchun jarima qancha?"}],["$","$L48",null,{"children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"O'z vaqtida to'lamaganlik uchun har bir kechiktirilgan kun uchun MB qayta moliyalash stavkasining 1/300 qismi miqdorida penya hisoblanadi (MB stavkasi 14% da — 0,047%/kun, yillik 17,0%)."}]}]]}],["$","$L46","7",{"value":"faq-7","children":[["$","$L47",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"Ish haqim mahalla orqali to'lansa, JShShS qanday ushlanadi?"}],["$","$L48",null,{"children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"Mahalla orqali rasmiy ish haqi to'lanadigan bo'lsa (masalan, ijtimoiy ish o'rinlari), to'lovchi tashkilot soliq agenti sifatida ishlaydi va 12% JShShSni o'zi ushlab qoladi. Sizning xatti-harakatingiz talab qilinmaydi."}]}]]}],["$","$L46","8",{"value":"faq-8","children":[["$","$L47",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"Frilanser bo'lsam, daromad solig'ini qanday to'layman?"}],["$","$L48",null,{"children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"2026-yildan boshlab samozanyat (o'z-o'zini band qilgan) shaxs sifatida ro'yxatdan o'tib,